<plot>Born in April 1999 with a rare form of muscular dystrophy condition called Nemaline Myopathy. Felix has the severest form and is on a ventilator, tube fed, uses a power wheelchair and has a whole set of issues arising from his profound muscle weakness. This film highlights Felix and his families day to day difficulties living and dealing with his circumstance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?009417</url></doc>
